  <h2>Model </h2>
  
<p>Our approach is to vectorize the sentences, where each unique word will be represented as a binary column, as shown in the next figure.</p>

<img src="/images/spam_detection/vector.svg" alt="">

<p>This enables us to treat each word as a numeric feature, allowing us to use Logistic Regression and Random Forest for classification.
</p>
